snippet.title: Dominique Pamplemousse: Trailer
snippet.description:
Dominique Pamplemousse in "It's All Over Once The Fat Lady Sings!"
Available on Windows, Mac, and iPad!

A unique and offbeat stop motion animated detective adventure game about gender and the economy. Also, all the characters frequently burst into song.

Nominated for four Independent Games Festival awards, including best game!

http://www.dominiquepamplemousse.com/
